Package: hydrologicalModelling
Title: Advanced Tools for Hydrological Modelling
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Eric", "Musonera", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Provides advanced tools for hydrological modelling, including functionalities for 
    snapping pour points to stream rasters, handling spatial data, and visualizing hydrological 
    features. The package integrates various methods and tools from spatial and hydrological 
    analyses to facilitate robust and efficient modelling processes.
